data.description: Charming 2-bed, 1-bath home offers ample natural light, 2 decks and a fenced in backyard. Main floor bath offers a tile shower and deep tub perfect for those relaxing baths during the colder winter months. Basement offers a bedroom with an office nook. Finish the rest of the basement off for additional square footage. The 1 car garage is spacious enough for a car and all the outside tools. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours!
